The JSON files under this directory are vendored verbatim from the CADBench
project, tested_models/{model}/{modality}/r1/bench{A,B,E,F,M,O}_results/ .

Only the AGGREGATE baseline metric outputs are vendored:
  * bench*_metrics.json           -- per-(model,modality,bench) overall scores
  * bench*_per_label_metrics.json -- the same, split easy/medium/hard

These are computed OUTPUTS of the MIT-licensed CADBench evaluation code
(Mean/Median/Std/Adjusted stats, VSR, Timeout Rate, code-size metrics). They
carry NO per-object dataset provenance (no file ids, no STEP/STL/image/mesh
content): they are eval numbers, not benchmark task data. The task data
(DeepCAD / Fusion360 / ABC / Objaverse / MCB derived STEP/STL/image/mesh) is
NOT vendored here -- it is HuggingFace-hosted, absent from the checkout, and
under a mixed/non-commercial license (see the repo's DATASET_LICENSE.md).

